{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Churban_Reunion_of_Sorts",
  "title": "A Churban Reunion of Sorts",
  "summary": "In the rotating Infinity Restaurant atop Plaxton City on Caspar, Senator Di'anCecht, his pregnant wife Jessalyn, the artist Kendell, and the Horansi cub Kuxli share a quiet evening that is interrupted when Piper arrives with her dog Duke and the Caspian pilot Rtufo strides in. When Piper unexpectedly speaks Churban, Rtufo is electrified to discover a fellow speaker of his nearly-extinct language, and the two trade barbed exchanges in their native tongue. Di'anCecht reveals that 'Piper' is in fact Simone Drake, a Vice President of the Corporate Sector, while Jessalyn, increasingly unwell from her pregnancy, slips away to the elevator for air. Rtufo accuses the woman of abandoning her Churban heritage, only for the confrontation to soften into recognition when Piper deduces he is the brother of a woman named Dannan and the missing Doron. The reunion is cut short before resolution when the player controlling Rtufo loses connection to the MUSH.",
